# AI Rules for this project

- Always use the latest MUI syntax, in this case v7, specifically for the <Grid size={{xs:1, md:2}}> component, see https://mui.com/material-ui/react-grid/
- Only use MUI, no HTML unless it is needed for e.g. HTML5 landmarks, take inspiration from MUI Toolpad for the set up
- Site needs to be fully WCAG2.2 AA compatible for accessibility
- Site needs to be fully responsive
- Make use of the MUI theme only, no overrides unless absolutely necessary
- Keep the code as simple as possible, no unnecessary complexity
- use the vanilla installation of https://opennext.js.org/cloudflare/get-started
- use the vanilla set up of https://nextjs.org/docs/app/guides/mdx